{"tid":1349700,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人快啲認清事實 (和理非)","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:03:58.000Z","uid":281039,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ca53c0e58b5d7547ed276b3d4bcaef3b9df802","tid":1349700,"uid":281039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">經過尋日天水圍同中環發生嘅事，今時今日仲諗住用和理非出聲嘅人，得罪講句根本唔清楚而家嘅局況，唔好誤會，我好欣賞和理非，因為和理非係遊行人士質素嘅體現。<br />\n但係當你嘅敵人都唔遵守規則嘅時候，你同佢講規則，講道理，根本就對牛彈琴，仲會傷害你自己，因為簡單啲嚟講你就係喺度捱打。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當中環開36槍嘅時候</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwLRqyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwLRqyL.png&h=4b84b675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當黑社會介入政治事件嘅時候</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/806X5DJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F806X5DJ.jpg&h=46d869a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YkBBLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YkBBLz.jpg&h=96bcf04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當你嘅屋企人被人打到咁嘅時候</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rvJ1nN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rvJ1nN.png&h=1445d65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當大肚婆都可以落手嘅時候</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kn9OsQn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn9OsQn.png&h=6ed5e677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當犬隻冇良心到隻眼開隻眼閉，擰轉頭走人，坐視不理嘅時候</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cb2cUx8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcb2cUx8.png&h=c57a458a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再同我講用和理非出聲，唔好再同我講警察只係打份工，唔好再同我講政府都讓咗步，你仲想點?</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港人成日好善忘，好快就對事件麻木，聽日繼續返工。但係一定要記住呢個政府點對你，同由6月9號開始發生嘅事。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">依家係勇武出嚟嘅時候，香港淨係得香港人可以自己救。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個係許勝不許敗嘅一場仗，因為一輸咗，我哋呢個地方就冇㗎喇 !!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做，不割蓆，不篤灰，和而不同，互相扶持</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgL9WXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgL9WXF.png&h=996bf76e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">BE WATER，MY FAMILY</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7d9f378625018acccd7dc7710eecbed6a9a7e9a","tid":1349700,"uid":277144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:56:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"ff0b6cb076ba80fcddd14c656b04467fd975bdfd","tid":1349700,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"幫手推，宜家係關鍵時期動搖淺藍民意！<br />\n<br />\n【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6af7eb058256b1d9295e222926a4742296b87ac0","tid":1349700,"uid":281039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"明明預覽嗰陣好地地，點解po咗出嚟之後會褪曬位 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2042ae3f9fff3df65450cb28fee4a7698b34ff9","tid":1349700,"uid":281039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"16c0d3e4a31c1acc56963b91babecfbaa5a5df0